# For latitudes and longitudes, get the closest value in the data for input coordinates

lonvals = cds.longitude[:]
latvals = cds.latitude[:]

def find_nearest(array, value):
    array = np.asarray(array)
    idx = (np.abs(array - value)).argmin()
    return array[idx]

# Pacific Ocean Coordinates
lnv = find_nearest(lonvals, 125) # closest longitude value
ltv = find_nearest(latvals, 8.7) #closes latitude value
print('Pacific Ocean Coordinates:')
print(lnv, lat.units)
print(ltv, lon.units)

# Convert to x-array DataArray type (with nans)
sal_Matt_arr = xr.DataArray(sal_Matt_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
hsal_Matt_arr = xr.DataArray(hsal_Matt_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
spd_Matt_arr = xr.DataArray(spd_Matt_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
hspd_Matt_arr = xr.DataArray(hspd_Matt_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
temp_Matt_arr = xr.DataArray(temp_Matt_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])

# Drop Nan Values from the not sea surface

hsalMatt_arr = hsal_Matt_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')
spdMatt_arr = spd_Matt_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')
hspdMatt_arr = hspd_Matt_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')
tempMatt_arr = temp_Matt_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')

# Convert xrArrays to xrDatasets
sal_Matt_ds = salMatt_arr.to_dataset(name= 'SSS')
hsal_Matt_ds = hsalMatt_arr.to_dataset(name= 'HSSS')
spd_Matt_ds = spdMatt_arr.to_dataset(name= 'SPD')
hspd_Matt_ds = hspdMatt_arr.to_dataset(name= 'HSPD')
temp_Matt_ds = tempMatt_arr.to_dataset(name= 'Temp')

# Merge xrDatasets
Mathew_ds = xr.merge([sal_Matt_ds,hsal_Matt_ds,spd_Matt_ds,hspd_Matt_ds,temp_Matt_ds]) # New Data Set

# Convert the merged xrDatasets into Pandas Dataframe
Matthew_df = Mathew_ds.to_dataframe(dim_order=['latitude', 'longitude', 'time'])

sal_Irm_arr = xr.DataArray(sal_Irm_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
hsal_Irm_arr = xr.DataArray(hsal_Irm_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
spd_Irm_arr = xr.DataArray(spd_Irm_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
hspd_Irm_arr = xr.DataArray(hspd_Irm_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])
temp_Irm_arr = xr.DataArray(temp_Irm_vals,dims = ["time","latitude","longitude"])

# Drop Nan Values from the not sea surface
salIrm_arr = sal_Irm_arr.dropna(dim='longitude') # Selecting along latitude dimension gives an error for some reason
hsalIrm_arr = hsal_Irm_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')
spdIrm_arr = spd_Irm_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')
hspdIrm_arr = hspd_Irm_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')
tempIrm_arr = temp_Irm_arr.dropna(dim='longitude')

# Convert xrArrays to xrDatasets
sal_Irm_ds = salIrm_arr.to_dataset(name= 'SSS')
hsal_Irm_ds = hsalIrm_arr.to_dataset(name= 'HSSS')
spd_Irm_ds = spdIrm_arr.to_dataset(name= 'SPD')
hspd_Irm_ds = hspdIrm_arr.to_dataset(name= 'HSPD')
temp_Irm_ds = tempIrm_arr.to_dataset(name= 'Temp')

# Merge xrDatasets
Irma_ds = xr.merge([sal_Irm_ds,hsal_Irm_ds,spd_Irm_ds,hspd_Irm_ds,temp_Irm_ds]) # New Data Set

# Convert the merged xrDatasets into Pandas Dataframe
Irma_df = Irma_ds.to_dataframe(dim_order=['latitude', 'longitude', 'time'])
